"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-athletics-2024-0529-1452036-the-silver-secret-treacys-olympic-marathon-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Have you heard the one about the Irishman who won an Olympic silver medal in his first ever marathon?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"40 years ago this August, John Treacy did just that, stunning the athletics world at the Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Treacy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Treacy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Waterford man was best known as a cross-country, 5,000 and 10,000-metre runner, and had put in 20k of hard running to finish ninth in the latter event six days previously.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\", \"score\": 0.9539459571200327, \"rank\": 0.0477191424052153, \"text\": \"Waterford\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waterford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Entering an event the 27-year-old had never competed in, it might have seemed like an afterthought or insurance policy.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, secretly, it was the target all along.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having moved back to his college town of Providence, Rhode Island the previous autumn in a bid to reignite his running career, Treacy resumed training with his former college coach Bob Amato's group and was introduced to Argentinian cardiologist and marathon runner Dr Dario Herrera.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"score\": 0.9999768590168074, \"rank\": 2.266567194867934e-05, \"text\": \"Providence\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"score\": 0.9999542871281314, \"rank\": 3.77155124092738e-05, \"text\": \"Rhode Island\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.9020824540106664, \"rank\": 0.052480011105261085, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giuliano_Amato\", \"score\": 0.9999986168455068, \"rank\": 1.3781942066276749e-06, \"text\": \"Amato\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giuliano_Amato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giuliano_Amato\"}, {\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.7442365642046026, \"rank\": 0.2320952960067369, \"text\": \"Argentinian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Herrera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dario Herrera\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Herrera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dario_Herrera\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Providence, at that particular time, we had a bunch of guys all training very well,\\\" Treacy tells Greg Allen onChapters of Magnificence, a new RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 series profiling 11 of Ireland's living Olympic medallists.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"score\": 0.9999768590168074, \"rank\": 2.266567194867934e-05, \"text\": \"Providence\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\"}, {\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Allen_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.8388139912274463, \"rank\": 0.1921568627450381, \"text\": \"Greg Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Allen_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Allen_(baseball)\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996812221, \"rank\": 3.184307701082103e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Around that time, we were doing our VO2 max and efficiency and Dr Hererra said to me 'Listen, everything is pointing to this marathon'.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I said: 'I do not want to do the marathon.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to go back, I have unfinished business in 10,000 metres.'\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it took a bit of persuasion to get to the marathon.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The other thing that was weighing on my mind was 'Los Angeles\\u2026 marathon\\u2026 heat\\u2026 how could I cope with that?\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.783649503121012e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In fairness, Dario did a lot of research in terms of heat acclimatisation and really got his homework done in terms of what I needed to do.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As it happened, during the month of June, Providence was roasting hot, so I was training in really hot weather.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"score\": 0.9999768590168074, \"rank\": 2.266567194867934e-05, \"text\": \"Providence\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Providence_College\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The preparation was excellent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need your consent to load this SoundCloud contentWe use SoundCloud to manage extra content that can set cookies on your device and collect data about your activity.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SoundCloud\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SoundCloud\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please review their details and accept them to load the content.Manage Preferences  Treacy had decided to still try to win a medal in the 10,000m before the marathon but kept the focus on his track running by setting some scorching 5,000m times that June.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 2182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always liked to race myself into world-class running.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I came back to Europe, maybe 10 days before I came back I did a 29-mile run on a really hot night.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I ran a 5k in London, 13:33 and four days later I ran 13:16 and beat Eamonn's [Coghlan] Irish record.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999989834987609, \"rank\": 1.0162815413078028e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had got myself in fabulous shape and really was ready to roll in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.783649503121012e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kept it all very quiet in terms of what I was doing.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always going to wind up running the marathon, there was no doubt about that, but it was just making sure I had the work done before I ran a marathon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to the Paris 2024 Olympic Games and marking 100 years of Ireland competing as an independent nation, RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 is broadcasting 'Chapters of Magnificence' a series of 11 radio programmes, each focusing on a living Irish medallist.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996812221, \"rank\": 3.184307701082103e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999639010383574, \"rank\": 3.601930678012563e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to the John Treacy episode on RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 on Sunday 2 June from 7.30-8pm and listen back to all the episodeshereafter broadcast  \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3165, \"end\": 3188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3190, \"end\": 3197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996812221, \"rank\": 3.184307701082103e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3231, \"end\": 3234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3318, \"end\": 3323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999549018072256, \"rank\": 2.5796727561955085e-05, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}]}"